      "suggestedVersionCode": "28",
      "description": "Nova AI \u2014 Multi-provider support with saved provider profiles, models.dev browser, and OpenCode Zen free models.\n\nFeatures:\n* Save multiple providers and switch between them instantly\n* Each provider remembers its API key, model list, and selected model\n* Browse 80+ OpenAI-compatible providers from models.dev\n* Fetch available models from any provider\n* Free models work without an API key (OpenCode Zen)\n* Streaming with reasoning/thinking display\n* Tool calling: calculator, time, web search (SearXNG)\n* Image vision\n* Clean bottom sheet UI\n* Markdown with tables, code blocks, lists\n* No tracking, no ads, no proprietary SDKs\n",
      "issueTracker": "https://github.com/loak7993-code/nova-ai/issues",
      "license": "GPL-3.0-or-later",
